{"tid":1125412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"46歲宮澤理惠爆懷孕! 出門穿這樣…嫩尪森田剛抱緊處理","createTime":"2019-04-25T16:28:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T04:09:17.000Z","uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5e230c8d06fef58dbf9707bb228f507ad230e944","tid":1125412,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T16:28:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RSq5ELS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRSq5ELS.jpg&h=5ad50240&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n46歲日本女星宮澤理惠懷孕了嗎？她4月臨時退出某部電影演出，讓劇組陷入一片慌亂之中，加上被拍到和小5歲老公森田剛外出時，身穿寬鬆連身裙，腳踩平底鞋，疑似懷孕的舉動引發外界好奇。<br />\n<br />\n據日媒《女性SEVEN》報導，宮澤理惠和森田剛於2018年3月結婚，加上10歲大的女兒，一家三口相當幸福，日前更被拍到和老公外出購物，身穿寬鬆連身裙，更有老公摟著肩膀、手腕攙扶著，牽手也不忘十指緊扣，互動相當甜蜜。她新婚生活美滿，工作上則傳出臨時取消演出，由於該片即將進入宣傳階段，造成相關單位不小困擾，損失尚無法估計。<br />\n<br />\n除了取消演出，宮澤理惠早前被目擊進出婦產科醫院，被爆正在接受不孕治療。知情人士透露，她非常想要為森田剛生孩子，於是減少工作，打從2017年取消主演舞台劇開始，就傳出準備結婚懷孕，婚後又推掉電影片約，加上夫妻倆被拍到外出購物時，愛抽菸的老公全程不抽菸，讓懷孕傳言再次傳開，對此她的經紀公司表示「負責人不在無法回應。」"},{"pid":"80ac074aebada21fa53453ea364e3e77861a94b2","tid":1125412,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T16:34:39.000Z","msg":"幾型下，唔係個個carry到"},{"pid":"c95adf0810b357e103adda60a3dd2ea8355428a7","tid":1125412,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T20:38:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d664492b4c86359079ac074995b5061eff45c0a","tid":1125412,"uid":5591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T20:47:13.000Z","msg":"貴花田呢？"},{"pid":"cd94787e633cfd533fad182e1f87186e16c9432e","tid":1125412,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T20:50:14.000Z","msg":"個樣好老"},{"pid":"cb28af27b0e8e90c8c387f15cb553fa0b629f101","tid":1125412,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T20:51:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3a6e6a30688ff7f1214c4f59d1e3dd37e4c6d0b5","tid":1125412,"uid":140309,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T21:12:28.000Z","msg":"男人個樣好頹"},{"pid":"aabb3cd3cc0edfd749eef8129286681a1115c80b","tid":1125412,"uid":51532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T23:09:09.000Z","msg":"第一代金田一一個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b22547feb1b39251930a3f1e2e043f9f309f037","tid":1125412,"uid":86980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aabb3cd3cc0edfd749eef8129286681a1115c80b","tid":1125412,"uid":51532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T23:09:09.000Z","msg":"第一代金田一一個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T23:14:06.000Z","msg":"唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰個係堂本剛"},{"pid":"1308d62ffe24460140805e78de35affb8435fa0b","tid":1125412,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T00:46:43.000Z","msg":"美雪好慘"},{"pid":"6cde403f4c8bd465f5f97bfbfb215f098e1c8554","tid":1125412,"uid":221265,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T00:55:30.000Z","msg":"2人全盛期<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n森田剛得163cm又係矮仔<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9sRHKNn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9sRHKNn.png&h=233dbd0a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http